data.description: Package Deal with 92 Coale Ave (second lot) is 20x100 totaling to 60x100. Currently 20x100 is being used as private parking with garage that can park up to 8 vehicles. The residence boasts a generously sized 40x100 lot, with ample front and back yards that provide plenty of space for year-round activities. A full and finished basement boasts a family room and laundry room can be found on the property. On the first level, there is a living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, one bedroom, and a full bathroom. The second level includes a living room, eat-in kitchen, one bedroom, and another full bathroom. Additionally, a walk-up finished attic with a cozy gas fireplace is also available. There’s a side entrance to access the first floor and basement. The property has a new boiler installed in 2022, as well as a heater that is 12 years old and a roof that is 17 years old. Situated in close proximity to shops and public transportation, this home is an ideal location for commuting within the city.
